name: Dotlinker
body:
### Welcome to Dotlinker ImageJ plugin. 

The plugin is still under development.

The aim of this project is to provide solutions for wide variety of "Dots" tracking: by Dots I mean any type of objects found in biological system.  

### Downloads

Here is the [download link to the Jar file](https://github.com/cmci/DotLinker/blob/gh-pages/target/Dot_Linker-1.0.0.jar?raw=true). 

### Documentation

Currently not available, [but here is the javadoc](http://cmci.github.com/DotLinker/doc/index.html). 

### Authors and Contributors

Kota Miura (@cmci)
